{"tid":1884984,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"光復咗香港之後，你想成為一個點樣嘅人？","createTime":"2020-02-18T03:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T12:37:46.000Z","uid":211994,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dcebe0faad334f09c2547566b822e2f3ed76ea34","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知，我地距離目標仲有一大大大大大段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家講呢樣好似太早，甚至喺呢個「<span style=\"color: red;\">好似</span>大家團火熄咗」嘅氛圍下，我可能會比人鬧我太天真添。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但事實係，人要有一個目標，先會有動力行落去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，好多人都係唔想辜負手足嘅犧牲先繼續抗爭落去，但對大部分人嚟講，要一直記住呢八個月嘅痛苦，對於心理健康嚟講的確唔太好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我唔係想否定呢種推動自己嘅方法，因為我自己都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n所以我呢個痴線佬想喺連登宣播少少正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當成功光復香港，我地可以票選自己嘅領袖，產業結構更加多元化，香港民族嘅意識終於成形；<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔需要活喺政權同警暴嘅恐懼下，唔需要再戴頭盔豬嘴整熄粒催淚彈，唔會再有人失蹤。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺完成咗任務之後，你想開拓一個點樣嘅人生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我開始先：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我想揸住香港國嘅護照，好自豪咁向呢個世界介紹自己嘅家鄉</span><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"639637f35e68b00fb0450b80b0888b0a2a161f64","tid":1884984,"uid":66254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"軍人"},{"pid":"a5880cfe57b13b1dbfba4c2dd70d554f49265db9","tid":1884984,"uid":221571,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:27:43.000Z","msg":"「香港人」<br />\n<br />\n完，我冇野講。"},{"pid":"360d858917245ef841cee3cdb5c9fd4fec5b3216","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"我都係睇完呢個po先有呢個諗法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwOt9D8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwOt9D8.png&h=57246ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35d19a6c2f354cc0e10b95271643f30c428c7f1e","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"207c0f3b7195cc6db30b6f7f3638ab560d338980","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c25cc90aa7994175fd3ffc072e95b4a0b43eaa9","tid":1884984,"uid":52859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791e6a4cfc3f184c4a87759229bfe4f2be8b1394","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45589ebe340b299750ab8e44922bfbc42abac5fb","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"30accbc7b13531c414a4b7bbf1ed36c530a3c808","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3b4d238d4b5bc194701dd024a12bd7a4463e89f4","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:30:39.000Z","msg":"Tui<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e5d2fa2f4e9cbdd9470407d6b774728b177d13","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7770a9b3bbdf044cf7b8eaa18bb40af36855691","tid":1884984,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"